## Scientific Research Projects:  

1. In 2000, he participated in the "Research on Social Network and Mental Health" (in cooperation with The Chinese University of Hong Kong); 

2. From 1999 to 2000, he presided over the "Research on World Bank Beijing Environment Project" (in cooperation with the World Bank); 

3. In 1998, he presided over the "(Lifestyle), (China Business News) series of research"; 

4. In 1997, he participated in "Research on Social Network"; 

5. In 1997, he presided over the "Hope Project Evaluation Project" (in cooperation with China Youth Development Foundation); 

6. In 1997, he presided over the "Research on Chinese Reading Life of Twenty Years"; 

7. In 1997, he participated in the "Research on Higher Income Community Lifestyle"; 

8. From 1992 to 1996, he participated in the "Research on District Economy and Community Development" (in cooperation with Shenhe District Government, Shenyang City); 

9. From 1996 to 1998, he participated in the "Research on Migrant Workers"; 

10. In 1998, he presided over the "Credit Research"; 

12. In 2000, he participated in the "Research on Migrant Population" (in cooperation with America); 

13. In 1996, he participated in the "Research on Chinese Entrepreneur" (in cooperation with EU); 

14. From 1992 to 1993, he presided over the "Research on Chinese Wholesale Market" (in cooperation with Shenhe District Government, Shenyang City); 

15. In 2000, he presided over the "Research on Post and Telecommunication System" (in cooperation with Beijing International Post Office); 

16. In 2001, he continued to presided over the "Research on World Bank Beijing Environment Project" (in cooperation with the World Bank). 

17. In 2001, he presided over the "Research on Beijing Newspaper Retail Sale Market"; 

18. In 2001, he participated in the "Research on the Culture Development Strategy of China Life";
